data.description: ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE! Centrally located just minutes from Mid-City, Uptown/Carrolton, and Old Metairie, come home to an expansive front porch, loads of off-street parking, and an open, functional floor plan. Renovated in 2018 and only 11 years young. Quartz counters, wood laminate and tile throughout, a three year old central air system, and tons of smart home features. Streets are in the process of being paved and the best news of all THIS LOAN CAN BE ASSUMED AT AN INTEREST RATE UNDER 3% (for qualified buyers)!!! --X Flood Zone.
